      <title>马来西亚法院命令纳吉为更多 1MDB 指控进行辩护</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/malaysia-court-orders-ex-pm-najib-to-defend-more-1mdb-charges</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚高等法院命令前总理纳吉布拉扎克针对与主权财富基金 1MDB 相关的腐败和洗钱指控为自己辩护，这对这位已经因丑闻入狱的政治家来说是又一次打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-30/malaysia-court-orders-ex-pm-najib-to-defend-more-1mdb-charges</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 03:04:42 GMT</pubDate>
